nnsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00907">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [20. 3. 1899]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L00909">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [23. 3. 1899]</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00907">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [20. 3. 1899]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L00909">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, [23. 3. 1899]</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
